NAME
    Lingua::Cyrillic::Translit::ICAO -- Cyrillic characters transliteration
    into ICAO Doc 9303

SYNOPSIS
     use Lingua::Cyrillic::Translit::ICAO qw/ cyr2icao /;

     print cyr2icao('ukrainian', 'koi8-r');

DESCRIPTION
    Lingua::UK::Translit::ICAO can be used for transliteration of Cyrillic
    characters in conformance with ICAO Doc 9303 Recommendations.

METHODS
  cyr2icao ( $string, [$language], [ $encoding ])
    This method converts $string from Cyrillic character set to ICAO
    transliteration.

    Optional $language parameter allow to specify $string's language. Valid
    values are:

    'by' - Belorussian
    'bu' - Bulgarian
    'mk' - Macedonian
    'uk' - Ukrainian

    Other values are accepted but do not affect anything.

    Optional $encoding parameter allows to specify $string's encoding
    (default is 'utf-8')

